<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f4f4f6;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#f4f4f6; padding:32px 0;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:600px; width:100%; background-color:#ffffff; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden; font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background-color:#e6007e; padding:28px 32px;">
                            <h1 style="margin:0; color:#ffffff; font-size:22px; line-height:1.3;">Neue Lieferanfrage</h1>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding:32px;">
                            <p style="margin:0 0 8px; color:#1f2440; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6;">
                                Über den Preisrechner ist eine neue Lieferanfrage eingegangen.
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin:0 0 24px; color:#8a8a99; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6;">
                                Der Gesamtpreis ist eine <strong>Schätzung aus dem Rechner</strong> - bitte den exakten Preis prüfen und der anfragenden Person bestätigen.
                            </p>

                            {% set field = 'Zustellzeit' %}
                            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; margin-bottom:24px;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding:12px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #ececf0; color:#8a8a99; font-size:13px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.04em; width:42%;">Zustellzeit</td>
                                    <td style="padding:12px 0 12px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #ececf0; color:#1f2440; font-size:16px;">{{ values.deliveryTime }}</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding:12px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #ececf0; color:#8a8a99; font-size:13px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.04em;">Geschätzter Gesamtpreis</td>
                                    <td style="padding:12px 0 12px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #ececf0; color:#1f2440; font-size:16px;">{{ values.estimatedTotal ?: '-' }} <span style="color:#8a8a99; font-size:13px;">(Schätzung)</span></td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <h2 style="margin:0 0 12px; color:#1f2440; font-size:18px;">Route &amp; Adressen</h2>
                            <div style="background-color:#f7f7f9; border-radius:8px; padding:16px 20px; color:#1f2440; font-size:15px; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:24px; white-space:pre-wrap;">{{ values.stops }}</div>

                            <h2 style="margin:0 0 12px; color:#1f2440; font-size:18px;">Kunde</h2>
                            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; margin-bottom:24px;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #ececf0; color:#8a8a99; font-size:13px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.04em; width:42%;">Name</td>
                                    <td style="padding:10px 0 10px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #ececf0; color:#1f2440; font-size:16px;">{{ values.name }}</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #ececf0; color:#8a8a99; font-size:13px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.04em;">E-Mail</td>
                                    <td style="padding:10px 0 10px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #ececf0; color:#1f2440; font-size:16px;"><a href="mailto:{{ values.email }}" style="color:#e6007e; text-decoration:none;">{{ values.email }}</a></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #ececf0; color:#8a8a99; font-size:13px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.04em;">Telefon</td>
                                    <td style="padding:10px 0 10px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #ececf0; color:#1f2440; font-size:16px;">{{ values.phone }}</td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <h2 style="margin:0 0 12px; color:#1f2440; font-size:18px;">Rechnungsanschrift</h2>
                            <p style="margin:0 0 24px; color:#1f2440; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6;">
                                {{ values.company ?: values.name }}<br>
                                {{ values.billingStreet }}<br>
                                {{ values.billingZip }} {{ values.billingCity }}
                            </p>

                            {% if values.notes %}
                                <h2 style="margin:0 0 12px; color:#1f2440; font-size:18px;">Nachricht</h2>
                                <p style="margin:0 0 24px; color:#1f2440; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6;">{{ values.notes|nl2br }}</p>
                            {% endif %}

                            <p style="margin:28px 0 0; color:#8a8a99; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6;">
                                Antwort auf diese E-Mail geht direkt an die anfragende Person.
                                Die Anfrage liegt außerdem im CMS unter &bdquo;Anfragen&ldquo;.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
